Package: EcoTherm
Type: Package
Title: Optimizing Thermal Efficiency and Reducing Environmental Impact
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("DONALD", "FOGANG", email = "donaldfogang@gmail.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: EcoTherm is a comprehensive R package designed to optimize 
  thermal processes in energy production while minimizing environmental impact. 
  It provides a suite of functions for calculating enthalpy changes, 
  visualizing data trends, analyzing efficiency, forecasting profits, 
  and recommending emission reduction strategies. 
  This package aims to support thermal power plants in enhancing their operational efficiency and sustainability.
